    {
      "chinese": "因此，部落須有可凝聚烏合之眾的組織，族人了解彼此的身分和責任，分爲平民和貴族階級，也生成不同故事和規範。族人必須明白、重視部落組織的意義和價值。",
      "ab": "Ala ngualay kikay alapaacegecege kudra lrimaka paelreelre ki ngiasarade ku laumaumase, mathingathingale ku tasakayyane ku apasikaikayyane ki cekele, alatualay kikay ikaynga kikay lakaukawlu si talialaalay niiyane, lamakaelaela ku taabuubulruane si tasiluludane, lakamani ku atukucingalrane madu, thingale ku paluludane si patharevane ki tamadaredarepane ikay ki cekele.",
